<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Thusim chu gen ka nuom hi,
 Muh loh chunglam thusim; Isu leh A lopi zie,
 Leh A hehpihna thu!
 Thusim chuh gen ka nuom hi,
 A dik ka het ziekin;
 Ka utna a hih bukim,
 Thildang hih theih loh chuh.

[V2]
 Thusim chuh gen ka nuom hi!
 Ka thupi pen chuh hina;
 Thusim lui tak gen ding chuh,
 Isu hehpihna thu!

[V3]
 2. Thusim chuh gen ka nuom hi,
 Mak deuh deuha lang chuh; thildang ngaihtuohna cheng sang,
 Leh zanmang sang inle;
 Thusim chuh gen ka nuom hi,
 Kei dinga pha pen chuh;
 Aziek chuh ziechu ahi,
 Tu'n nang ka hun hilh chuh.

[V4]
 3. Thusim chuh gen ka nuom hi!
 Gen kit zel a nuom hi! ka gen chengin hawih deuh deuh,
 Mak deuh deuh in alang;
 Thusim chuh gen ka nuom hi,
 Mi kimkhat zak ngei loh;
 Hukdamna thu chuh ahi,
 Pathien Thu Thieng apat.

[V5]
 4. Thusim chuh gen ka nuom hi,
 A phat zie hete di'n; gilkiel, dangchak thuok laia,
 Chawlhna nuom bang ahi;
 Lopina mun ka tun tieng,
 La THAK chuh sa'ng ka ting;
 Ziechuh THUSIM LUI hina,
 Ka deih mah mah zing chuh!</lyrics>
<title>I LOVE TO TELL THE STORY</title>
</song>